	//Description  		: Enables The User To Send Mail 
	//Input Parameter 	: logval: To Indicate The Value Of The Logger To Be Used (Parent Or Child Logger), RMAApp_SendMail_Txt_To - Recipient Email ID, CCEmailID - Copy To Email ID, ObjDesc: Description Of The Page Where Send Mail Functionality Is To Be Tested
