	//Input Parameter 	: Entity: Indicates The Type Of Entity To Be Created, ClaimEvent: ClaimNumber Or Event Number To Which The Entity Needs To Be Added, ClaimEntity: Created Entity Name To Be Returned From The Function Of Type String, Intlogval Of Type Integer
	//Revision			: 0.0 - Jannathhussain-04-05-2018     
